00:23:21.799 --> 00:23:25.870
by. If it's something else, maybe I just worry
that I'm too late in life. I should've done

00:23:25.870 --> 00:23:31.150
this years ago or whatever. And I think it's
really interesting because I always say it's

00:23:31.150 --> 00:23:35.440
good to do market research, it's good to think
about your motivations and understand what

00:23:35.440 --> 00:23:39.520
you really want to do and if you're gonna
stick with it. And all those things are great,

00:23:39.520 --> 00:23:44.160
