place to make that come about. So, I think

00:33:11.659 --> 00:33:15.240
it’s good to have conversations. I think
it’s good to have joint planning sessions.

00:33:15.240 --> 00:33:19.520
It’s good to find a way to support each
other’s dreams. What's up?

00:33:19.520 --> 00:33:21.950
&gt;&gt;Male audience #3: Hi, Chris. I'm Ryan.

00:33:21.950 --> 00:33:22.950
&gt;&gt;Chris: Hi Ryan.

00:33:22.950 --> 00:33:25.740
&gt;&gt;audience #3: Speaking of families, I was
curious what your upbringing was like that

00:33:25.740 --> 00:33:28.919
pushed you into this obsession with nonconformity?

00:33:28.919 --> 00:33:36.309
&gt;&gt;Chris: About my upbringing. Well, I had
