00:39:48.550 --> 00:39:52.839
there? Or do you find that when you find a
groove, you really hit it and you're motivated

00:39:52.839 --> 00:39:54.099
from the start?

00:39:54.099 --> 00:39:58.470
&gt;&gt;Chris: For the most part, I enjoy almost
